</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170926103854dhN6kAJvsuSzFixB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092610385412O7RWdvrmyIfJKA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Rihanna 的个人美妆品牌 Fenty Beauty 通过官方 Instagram 发布了一组 <a href=\"https://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/fenty-beauty-launched-holiday-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Holiday Collection </a>的图片，来看看： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170926102754OUqVmi6dBxwHonGN.png\" data-ratio=\"0.929878\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170926102750GkLI4Bs3xYjXEUhC.png\" data-ratio=\"0.995413\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092610274943uUljAsRXdwSzJK.png\" data-ratio=\"0.996942\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170926102750vSjbpTlLn2Mk47Ns.png\" data-ratio=\"1.163609\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>这周四，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/25/fenty-puma-by-rihanna-fw17/#slide-5\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fenty Puma </a>的 2017 秋冬系列将正式上架，这里有完整的单品图：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709261029487W51UF2DKxTyhZYd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709261029439Y3n4GmF5jeJKQxE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170926102947NPwiARLWJFXsqkMz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170926102941xvF49o7sAGq2tJYZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170926102942IBgSNstay